The '''Embassy of the State of Palestine''' in [[Oman]] ({{lang-ar|سفارة دولة فلسطين لدى سلطنة عمان}}) is the [[diplomatic mission]] of the [[State of Palestine|Palestine]] in Oman. It is located in [[Muscat Governorate|Muscat]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mofa.pna.ps/ar/archives/3334|title=Embassy of the State of Palestine in Oman|publisher=Ministry of foreign affairs of State of Palestine|accessdate=3 January 2017}}</ref>

