{{Infobox journal | title = Modern Theology | abbreviation = Mod. Theol. | discipline = [[Theology]] | publisher = [[Wiley-Blackwell]] | country = | history = 1984-present | frequency = Quarterly | open-access = | website = http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/10.1111/(ISSN)1468-0025 | editor = Jim Fodor, Bill Cavanaugh | ISSN = 0266-7177 | eISSN = 1468-0025 | OCLC = 11538889 | cover = ModernTheologyJournalCover.jpg | link1 = http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/10.1111/%28ISSN%291468-0025/currentissue | link1-name = Online access }} '''''Modern Theology''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by [[Wiley-Blackwell]]. It publishes [[Article (publishing)|articles]], review articles, and [[book reviews]] in the area of [[theology]], with an [[Ecumenism|ecumenical]] editorial policy.<ref name=info>{{cite web |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/10.1111/%28ISSN%291468-0025/homepage/ProductInformation.html |title=Modern Theology - Overview |publisher=[[Wiley-Blackwell]] |work=Wiley Online Library |accessdate=2010-11-07}}</ref>
